channel.title: Not another leecher
channel.description:
Hello,
I reinstalled SLR for like 4 times already but I'm still getting errors like the one mentioned in this topic (duplicate identifier, unknown identifier) Someone told me I should install the plugins, but I'm sure I got them installed
I successfully installed SRL but when I use a decent script for auto fletching I still get errors
I'm definitely sure I installed all includes and plugins I can imagine
error: Failed when compiling Line 1513: [Error] (15962:4): Unknown identifier 'FindDtmIn' in script F:\Program Files\SCAR 3.06\Scripts\BeastFletcher v0.43 [Not Obbed].scar
link to script: http://www.srl-forums.com/forum/rs2-srl-ejjman1s-t7108.html?s=d5e1bd963e89d396f1dcc2dfa0d3d4d0&t=7108

I hope anyone can help me!
Tnx allot Xtraxion

put your SRL Stats info, If you don’t have an SRL Stats account just comment SRLId and SRLPassword out:

item.title: Not another leecher
item.dc:creator: @Nashi Nashi
item.description:
@Nashi wrote:

Thats an error in the scripts, You’ve successfully installed SRL or it would of given you a different Error

at the top somewhere there should be “{.include SRL\SRL.scar}” underneath that put “{.include SRL\SRL\Extended\xDTM.scar}” That will fix the error your currently getting.

Should look like this:{.include SRL\SRL.scar} {.include SRL\SRL\Extended\xDTM.scar}
